This is GNU Rot[t]Log.
Archive, rotate, compress, and email system logs.

To install this program please read INSTALL.  See the info manual for
details on using this program.

Rot[t]log requires GNU coreutils, grep, gawk, and bash, and is intended
for the GNU system, (including Linux based GNU systems).  You should
also have an MTA for mail processing.
